(4406, 1, '2019-10-04 18:54:17', '2019-10-04 09:54:17', '<div class="l-content clearfix">\r\n<div class="l-container clearfix">\r\n<div class="l-sidenav">\r\n<ul class="p-sidenav-list">\r\n 	<li>\r\n<p class="l-sidenav-title"><a class="l-link l-link-underline is-pagelink" href="#philosophy">経営理念</a></p>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<p class="l-sidenav-title"><a class="l-link l-link-underline is-pagelink" href="#message">代表挨拶</a></p>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<p class="l-sidenav-title"><a class="l-link l-link-underline is-pagelink" href="#profile">会社概要</a></p>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<p class="l-sidenav-title"><a class="l-link l-link-underline is-pagelink" href="#history">沿革</a></p>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<p class="l-sidenav-title"><a class="l-link l-link-underline is-pagelink" href="#csr">CSR活動</a></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="sidenav-content" class="l-sidenav-content">\r\n<div class="l-sidenav-box">\r\n<h2 id="philosophy" class="m-titleH2 l-anchor">経営理念</h2>\r\n<h3 class="m-titleH3 m-sectionSmall tac">イワテックは、<br class="nopc" />5つの基本理念に基づき、\r\n同じベクトルで、社員一人ひとりが<br class="nopc" />社会へ貢献してまいります</h3>\r\n<p class="m-sectionMedium tac"><picture> <source srcset="http://iwatec.confirm-center-s2.com/wp-content/themes/iwatec/assets/images/about/img_philosophy_pc.jpg" media="(min-width:768px)" /></picture>\r\n<picture><source srcset="http://iwatec.confirm-center-s2.com/wp-content/themes/iwatec/assets/images/about/img_philosophy_sp.jpg" media="(max-width:767px)" /></picture>\r\n<picture><img class="imgswitch" src="http://iwatec.confirm-center-s2.com/wp-content/themes/iwatec/assets/images/about/img_philosophy_pc.jpg" alt="信頼 技術 環境 貢献 品質" /></picture></p>\r\n<!-- MESSAGE BEGIN -->\r\n<div class="m-sectionUltra">\r\n<h2 id="message" class="m-titleH2 l-anchor">代表挨拶</h2>\r\n<div class="p-message m-sectionSmall">\r\n<h3 class="p-message-txt m-titleH3">次世代に<br class="nopc" />継承するエネルギー、\r\n再生可能エネルギーが<br class="nopc" />その答えです。</h3>\r\n<picture> <source srcset="http://iwatec.confirm-center-s2.com/wp-content/themes/iwatec/assets/images/about/img_message_pc.jpg" media="(min-width:768px)" /></picture>\r\n<picture><source srcset="http://iwatec.confirm-center-s2.com/wp-content/themes/iwatec/assets/images/about/img_message_sp.jpg" media="(max-width:767px)" /></picture>\r\n<picture><img class="imgswitch" src="http://iwatec.confirm-center-s2.com/wp-content/themes/iwatec/assets/images/about/img_message_pc.jpg" alt="代表挨拶" /></picture>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="m-sectionMedium">\r\n<p class="m-txt">我々が住む、この美しい地球の悲鳴が聞こえてきています。\r\n温暖化現象による異常気象、北極・南極での氷の融け出しによる海面上昇など、\r\n挙げれば切りがありません。\r\n\r\n人間社会の化石燃料への依存過多、経済優先による無秩序な乱開発、今、我々人間は問われています。\r\n\r\n私たちの子供、孫、そしてその先の世代に残すべきエネルギー。\r\nその答えは、『再生可能エネルギー』です。\r\n\r\n決して遅くはありません。\r\n私たちイワテックは、正面から真剣に向かい合い、そのソリューションを形にしていきます。\r\n\r\n次世代に向かう『イワテック』と、一緒に手を取り合いませんか。</p>\r\n<p class="p-message-sign tar m-sectionMedium">代表取締役・最高経営責任者</p>\r\n<p class="tar mt10"><img src="http://iwatec.confirm-center-s2.com/wp-content/themes/iwatec/assets/images/about/ing_sign.png" alt="岩元考一郎" /></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- MESSAGE END -->\r\n\r\n<!-- PROFILE BEGIN -->\r\n<div class="m-sectionUltra">\r\n<h2 id="profile" class="m-titleH2 l-anchor">会社概要</h2>\r\n<table class="p-profile-table m-txt2 m-sectionMedium">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>商号</th>\r\n<td>株式会社イワテック</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>本社</th>\r\n<td>〒850-0045\r\n長崎県長崎市宝町7番5号 <br class="nopc" />第２イワテックビル\r\nTEL: 095-843-6448 <span class="nosp">/</span> <br class="nopc" />FAX: 095-843-6447\r\n<p class="m-btn m-sectionSmall"><a href="https://goo.gl/maps/zfv4MxAYQUkcu7CVA" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">MAPはこちら</a></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>設立</th>\r\n<td>平成元年(1989年) 4月</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>資本金</th>\r\n<td>2,000万円</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>取締役員</th>\r\n<td>代表取締役・最高経営責任者 <br class="nopc" />岩元 孝一郎\r\n取締役 岩元 亜子\r\n取締役 岩元 正信</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>建設業許可</th>\r\n<td>長崎県知事許可(特-26)第12915号</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>営業所</th>\r\n<td>\r\n<p class="fwm">久留米営業所</p>\r\n<p class="mt5">〒839-0809\r\n福岡県久留米市東合川3丁目2-17 <br class="nopc" />平成インタービル102号室\r\nTEL/FAX:0942-27-6437</p>\r\n<p class="m-btn m-sectionSmall"><a href="https://goo.gl/maps/i7SQachfPD5S7wBr9" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">MAPはこちら</a></p>\r\n<p class="fwm m-sectionSmall">インド支社</p>\r\n<p class="mt5">CD-135,Salt Lake City Sector I Kolkata－700 064,India</p>\r\n<p class="m-indent3">TEL：+91-33-2321-6732 <span class="nosp">/</span> 6733</p>\r\nFAX：+91-33-2321-6731\r\n\r\nE-mail：info@iwateccorp.com\r\n<p class="m-btn m-sectionSmall"><a href="https://goo.gl/maps/FCXKNBNG27eXtWum6" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">MAPはこちら</a></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>主要取引先</th>\r\n<td>\r\n<div class="half">\r\n<div class="half-item">\r\n<p class="fwm">国内</p>\r\n<p class="mt5">三菱日立パワーシステムズ株式会社\r\n株式会社MHPSコントロールシステムズ\r\n三菱重工業株式会社\r\n三菱電機株式会社\r\n三菱電機エンジニアリング株式会社</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="half-item">\r\n<p class="fwm">海外</p>\r\n<p class="mt5">ABB (スイス)\r\nSiemens (ドイツ)\r\nAlstom (フランス)\r\nBeckwith Electric (アメリカ)\r\nCummins (アメリカ，シンガポール)\r\nGUTOR (スイス)\r\nTEW (イギリス)\r\nDANIMEX (デンマーク)\r\nWILKEN (ケニア)\r\nRAYLEIGH (イギリス)\r\nRTK (イギリス)\r\nCEWE (スウェーデン)\r\nCROMPTON (イギリス)</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>主要金融機関</th>\r\n<td>株式会社親和銀行\r\n株式会社福岡銀行\r\n株式会社商工組合中央金庫\r\n株式会社日本政策金融公庫</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- PROFILE END -->\r\n\r\n<!-- HISTORY BEGIN -->\r\n<div class="m-sectionUltra">\r\n<h2 id="history" class="m-titleH2 l-anchor">沿革</h2>\r\n<div class="p-history m-sectionMedium">\r\n<div class="p-history-item">\r\n<div class="p-history-year">\r\n<p class="p-history-year-title">1989</p>\r\n<p class="p-history-year-sub">平成元年</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="p-history-content m-txt2 fwm">有限会社岩元設計事務所を設立\r\n海外部を組織し、各種電気品の海外調達体制を強化</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="p-history-item">\r\n<div class="p-history-year">\r\n<p class="p-history-year-title">1995</p>\r\n<p class="p-history-year-sub">平成7年</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="p-history-content m-txt2 fwm">イワテックビル 本社移転\r\n株式会社化し、社名を現在の『株式会社イワテック』へ変更</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="p-history-item">\r\n<div class="p-history-year">\r\n<p class="p-history-year-title">2003</p>\r\n<p class="p-history-year-sub">平成15年</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="p-history-content m-txt2 fwm">会社設立十五周年</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="p-history-item">\r\n<div class="p-history-year">\r\n<p class="p-history-year-title">2005</p>\r\n<p class="p-history-year-sub">平成17年</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="p-history-content m-txt2 fwm">コルカタにインド支社を設立\r\n「インディアエンジニアリングセンター」</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="p-history-item">\r\n<div class="p-history-year">\r\n<p class="p-history-year-title">2008</p>\r\n<p class="p-history-year-sub">平成20年</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="p-history-content m-txt2 fwm">会社設立二十周年\r\n太陽光発電事業に参入</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="p-history-item">\r\n<div class="p-history-year">\r\n<p class="p-history-year-title">2012</p>\r\n<p class="p-history-year-sub">平成24年</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="p-history-content m-txt2 fwm">ISO9001認証取得</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="p-history-item">\r\n<div class="p-history-year">\r\n<p class="p-history-year-title">2013</p>\r\n<p class="p-history-year-sub">平成25年</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="p-history-content m-txt2 fwm">久留米営業所開設\r\nO＆M事業に参入</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="p-history-item">\r\n<div class="p-history-year">\r\n<p class="p-history-year-title">2014</p>\r\n<p class="p-history-year-sub">平成26年</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="p-history-content m-txt2 fwm">イワテック第一・第二ソーラー発電所運転開始</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="p-history-item">\r\n<div class="p-history-year">\r\n<p class="p-history-year-title">2015</p>\r\n<p class="p-history-year-sub">平成27年</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="p-history-content m-txt2 fwm">イワテック第三・第四・第五ソーラー発電所運転開始\r\n水素・燃料電池事業に参入\r\n地熱・バイオマス・小水力を加えた、再生可能エネルギー事業に本格参入</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="p-history-item">\r\n<div class="p-history-year">\r\n<p class="p-history-year-title">2016</p>\r\n<p class="p-history-year-sub">平成28年</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="p-history-content m-txt2 fwm">第2イワテックビル 本社移転</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="p-history-item">\r\n<div class="p-history-year">\r\n<p class="p-history-year-title">2018</p>\r\n<p class="p-history-year-sub">平成30年</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="p-history-content m-txt2 fwm">会社設立三十周年\r\nイワテック第一温泉発電所運転開始</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- HISTORY END -->\r\n\r\n<!-- CSR BEGIN -->\r\n<div class="m-sectionUltra">\r\n<h2 id="csr" class="m-titleH2 l-anchor">CSR活動</h2>\r\n<ul class="p-csr m-sectionMedium">\r\n 	<li><img src="http://iwatec.confirm-center-s2.com/wp-content/themes/iwatec/assets/images/about/ing_cleaning.png" alt="社外清掃" />\r\n<p class="p-csr-txt">社外清掃</p>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li><img src="http://iwatec.confirm-center-s2.com/wp-content/themes/iwatec/assets/images/about/ing_inhouse.png" alt="自社発電所近隣自治会活動" />\r\n<p class="p-csr-txt">自社発電所近隣自治会活動</p>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li><img src="http://iwatec.confirm-center-s2.com/wp-content/themes/iwatec/assets/images/about/ing_sponsor.png" alt="地域イベントへの協賛" />\r\n<p class="p-csr-txt">地域イベントへの協賛</p>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li><a class="is-imghover" href="https://www.v-varen.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img src="http://iwatec.confirm-center-s2.com/wp-content/themes/iwatec/assets/images/about/ing_sport.png" alt="地域スポーツ振興事業" /></a>\r\n<p class="p-csr-txt">地域スポーツ振興事業</p>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li><img src="http://iwatec.confirm-center-s2.com/wp-content/themes/iwatec/assets/images/about/ing_donate.png" alt="熊本地震被災地への社用車寄付" />\r\n<p class="p-csr-txt">熊本地震被災地への社用車寄付</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- CSR END -->\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="clearfix">\r\n<div class="l-sidenav-content"><!-- CONTACT BEGIN -->\r\n<div class="m-contact">\r\n<h2 class="m-contact-title">CONTACT</h2>\r\n<p class="m-contact-sub">お問い合わせ</p>\r\n\r\n<ul class="m-contact-list clearfix">\r\n 	<li><a class="is-imghover" href="http://iwatec.confirm-center-s2.com/contact/" targe