AYLEIGH (イギリス)\r\nRTK (イギリス)\r\nCEWE (スウェーデン)\r\nCROMPTON (イギリス)</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<th>主要金融機関</th>\r\n<td>株式会社親和銀行\r\n株式会社福岡銀行\r\n株式会社商工組合中央金庫\r\n株式会社日本政策金融公庫</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="m-sectionUltra">\r\n<h2 id="history" class="m-titleH2 l-anchor">沿革</h2>\r\n<div class="p-history m-sectionMedium">\r\n<div class="p-history-item">\r\n<div class="p-history-year">\r\n<p class="p-history-year-title">1989</p>\r\n<p class="p-history-year-sub">平成元年</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="p-history-content m-txt2 fwm">有限会社岩元設計事務所を設立\r\n海外部を組織し、各種電気品の海外調達体制を強化</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="p-history-item">\r\n<div class="p-history-year">\r\n<p class="p-history-year-title">1995</p>\r\n<p class="p-history-year-sub">平成7年</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="p-history-content m-txt2 fwm">イワテックビル 本社移転\r\n株式会社化し、社名を現在の『株式会社イワテック』へ変更</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="p-history-item">\r\n<div class="p-history-year">\r\n<p class="p-history-year-title">2003</p>\r\n<p class="p-history-year-sub">平成元年</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="p-history-content m-txt2 fwm">会社設立十五周年</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="p-history-item">\r\n<div class="p-history-year">\r\n<p class="p-history-year-title">2005</p>\r\n<p class="p-history-year-sub">平成17年</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="p-history-content m-txt2 fwm">コルカタにインド支社を設立\r\n「インディアエンジニアリングセンター」</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="p-history-item">\r\n<div class="p-history-year">\r\n<p class="p-history-year-title">2008</p>\r\n<p class="p-history-year-sub">平成20年</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="p-history-content m-txt2 fwm">会社設立二十周年\r\n太陽光発電事業に参入</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="p-history-item">\r\n<div class="p-history-year">\r\n<p class="p-history-year-title">2012</p>\r\n<p class="p-history-year-sub">平成24年</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="p-history-content m-txt2 fwm">ISO9001認証取得</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="p-history-item">\r\n<div class="p-history-year">\r\n<p class="p-history-year-title">2013</p>\r\n<p class="p-history-year-sub">平成25年</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="p-history-content m-txt2 fwm">久留米営業所開設\r\nO＆M事業に参入</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="p-history-item">\r\n<div class="p-history-year">\r\n<p class="p-history-year-title">2014</p>\r\n<p class="p-history-year-sub">平成26年</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="p-history-content m-txt2 fwm">イワテック第一・第二ソーラー発電所運転開始</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="p-history-item">\r\n<div class="p-history-year">\r\n<p class="p-history-year-title">2015</p>\r\n<p class="p-history-year-sub">平成27年</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="p-history-content m-txt2 fwm">イワテック第三・第四・第五ソーラー発電所運転開始\r\n水素・燃料電池事業に参入\r\n地熱・バイオマス・小水力を加えた、再生可能エネルギー事業に本格参入</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="p-history-item">\r\n<div class="p-history-year">\r\n<p class="p-history-year-title">2016</p>\r\n<p class="p-history-year-sub">平成28年</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="p-history-content m-txt2 fwm">第2イワテックビル 本社移転</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="p-history-item">\r\n<div class="p-history-year">\r\n<p class="p-history-year-title">2018</p>\r\n<p class="p-history-year-sub">平成30年</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="p-history-content m-txt2 fwm">会社設立三十周年\r\nイワテック第一温泉発電所運転開始</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="m-sectionUltra">\r\n<h2 id="csr" class="m-titleH2 l-anchor">CSR活動</h2>\r\n<ul class="p-csr m-sectionMedium">\r\n 	<li><img title="社外清掃" src="http://iwatec.confirm-center-s2.com/wp-content/themes/iwatec/assets/images/about/ing_cleaning.png" alt="社外清掃" />\r\n<p class="p-csr-txt">社外清掃</p>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li><img title="自社発電所近隣自治会活動" src="http://iwatec.confirm-center-s2.com/wp-content/themes/iwatec/assets/images/about/ing_inhouse.png" alt="自社発電所近隣自治会活動" />\r\n<p class="p-csr-txt">自社発電所近隣自治会活動</p>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li><img title="地域イベントへの協賛" src="http://iwatec.confirm-center-s2.com/wp-content/themes/iwatec/assets/images/about/ing_sponsor.png" alt="地域イベントへの協賛" />\r\n<p class="p-csr-txt">地域イベントへの協賛</p>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li><a class="is-imghover" href="https://www.v-varen.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><img title="地域スポーツ振興事業" src="http://iwatec.confirm-center-s2.com/wp-content/themes/iwatec/assets/images/about/ing_sport.png" alt="地域スポーツ振興事業" /></a>\r\n<p class="p-csr-txt">地域スポーツ振興事業</p>\r\n</li>\r\n 	<li><img title="熊本地震被災地への社用車寄付" src="http://iwatec.confirm-center-s2.com/wp-content/themes/iwatec/assets/images/about/ing_donate.png" alt="熊本地震被災地への社用車寄付" />\r\n<p class="p-csr-txt">熊本地震被災地への社用車寄付</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', '会社案内', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '4406-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-10-17 15:47:47', '2019-10-17 06:47:47', '', 4406, 'http://iwatec.confirm-center-s2.com/2019/10/17/4406-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
